vcdimager: vcdimager (GNU vcd Imager)
vcdimager: 
vcdimager: VCDImager is a full-featured mastering suite for authoring, disassembling 
vcdimager: and analyzing Video CDs and Super Video CDs.The following 
vcdimager: features are available, support for Video CD 1.1 and 2.0 disc formats, 
vcdimager: support for the Super Video CD 1.0 disc format, full PBC (playback control) 
vcdimager: support (play lists, selection lists and end lists), support for segment
vcdimager: play items, automatic padding of MPEG streams on the fly, and support for 
vcdimager: 99-minute (out-of-specification) CD-R media
